                                 <p><strong>Day 08:</strong> Drive from Chopta to Sagar Village (Drive) – Same day trek to Pannar Bugyal.</p>
                                 <p><strong>Day 09:</strong> Trek from Pannar Bugyal to Rudranath and back to Pannar Bugyal. This would involve considerable distance and time as Rudranath is one of the Panch Kedar temples located at a higher altitude. Here’s a suggested itinerary for this trek:</p>
